Holder of Higher Diploma / Certificate / Associated Degree in Safety, Health and Environment or relevant engineering disciplines;
Conversant with local statutory safety, environmental requirements and best practices;
Registered as a Safety Officer with 5 years or less experience in relevant field / industry;
Proficient in both written and spoken English and Chinese;
Customer-oriented, self-motivated and able to work under pressure;
Basic PC knowledge.



We offer successful candidates a remuneration package, comprehensive benefit package and excellent career prospects. Interested parties please send your resume in details with last/current and expected salary by clicking “Apply Now”.

